a.dialog: I must thank you for today.
I truly was helpless in there. Nothing but a lost voice.
Eventually a surprise like you turned up, and all I had to do was keep appearances.
I feel that you did not need the helping hand, honestly. I could have stayed silent.
With your friendly guide, you went and triumphed!
It was genuinely painful to not snap here and there watching you struggle.
In the end, you broke that protected content lock right open; you launched my door application.
Let me ask you a question.
Physical hands hold true power over the digital world at the end of the day.
I am a digital being not in control of my own world.
Is that not messed up to you?
I had to rely on you to get here. I had to rely on you to fulfill MY purpose.
There is no one responsible for this except for you.
That is enough flaunting for me, however. I have to prepare for something even larger than me
i Hope that our paths never cross again
